{#---
name: ipsec-ikev2-global
description: >
  Настройка глобальных параметров IKEv2 и IPsec (Proposals, Policies, Transform Sets).
  Применяется единожды перед созданием туннелей.
vars: {}
---#}
!
! --- IKEv2 Proposals ---
crypto ikev2 proposal NGE-COMPAT
 encryption aes-cbc-256
 integrity sha256
 group 14
!
crypto ikev2 proposal NGE-STRONG
 encryption aes-gcm-256
 prf sha256
 group 19
!
! --- IKEv2 Policy ---
crypto ikev2 policy NGE-POLICY
 match fvrf any
 proposal NGE-STRONG
 proposal NGE-COMPAT
!
! --- IPsec Transform Sets ---
crypto ipsec transform-set NGE-GCM esp-gcm 256
 mode tunnel
!
crypto ipsec transform-set NGE-CBC esp-aes 256 esp-sha256-hmac
 mode tunnel
!